<li><a href="http://oee.nrcan.gc.ca/publications/infosource/home/index.cfm?act=online&amp;id=4427&amp;format=PDF&amp;lang=01&amp;PrintView=N&amp;Text=N" class="external text" title="http://oee.nrcan.gc.ca/publications/infosource/home/index.cfm?act=online&amp;id=4427&amp;format=PDF&amp;lang=01&amp;PrintView=N&amp;Text=N" rel="nofollow">Heating and Cooling with a Heat pump</a> - Information from the Canadian Government's Natural Resources Department, Office of Energy Efficiency</li>
</ul>


